data.description: Great opportunity to buy in the lovely Ridge Gate community of Murrieta! 2 bedroom, 1.75 bathroom floor plan. END UNIT single story, with patio views of the pool and nearby golf course. Spacious vaulted ceilings and lots of natural light throughout the home. Single car garage steps from the front door. HOA amenities include the swimming pool, spa, walking paths, and picnic areas. Convenient to shopping, schools, restaurants, and freeway access. Ready for new owners to make it their own!
